Targeted proteomics-derived biomarker profile develops a multi-protein 
classifier in liquid biopsies for early detection of esophageal squamous cell 
carcinoma from a population-based case-control study.

Yang X(#)(1)(2), Suo C(#)(3), Zhang T(4), Yin X(4), Man J(4), Yuan Z(5), Yu 
J(6), Jin L(5)(7), Chen X(8)(9), Lu M(10)(11)(12), Ye W(5)(6)(13).

Author information:
(1)Clinical Epidemiology Unit, Qilu Hospital of Shandong University, 107 
Wenhuaxi Road, Jinan, 250012, Shandong, China.
(2)Clinical Research Center of Shandong University, Qilu Hospital of Shandong 
